            <lg xml:id="TK505">
<l>perumaikku mēṉaic ciṟumaikkun tattaṅ</l>
<l> karumamē kaṭṭaḷaik kal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A man's deeds are the touchstone of his greatness and littleness.</l>
